Please install cloud-utils before starting:

sudo apt update
sudo apt install cloud-image-utils
sxhost +local:root

#################################  ATTACK  #####################################
In order to have graphical interface on Attack machine please install the packages:

sudo apt install --no-install-recommends xserver-xorg x11-xserver-utils xinit openbox
sudo apt install firefox-esr

After please setup the graphical environment:

inside ~/.xinitrc:

#!/bin/sh
openbox &
MOZ_FORCE_DISABLE_E10S=1 GTK_THEME=Adwaita:dark firefox --kiosk

To launch firefox:
startx

If not installed, please install npm next (not via apt install, from source)


To launch frontend:
- nohup npm run dev > out.log 2>&1 &
